# Trivy Security Scan Reports

This directory stores Trivy vulnerability scan reports for Docker images.

## Report Format

Reports are generated in both:
- `.txt` - Human-readable table format
- `.json` - Machine-parseable JSON format

## File Naming Convention

`<image-name>_<timestamp>.txt`

Example: `product-service_latest_20260111_143022.txt`

## Running Scans

See `scripts/trivy-scan.ps1` or `scripts/trivy-scan.sh`
